{"tid":2261461,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"自由黨調查：部分受訪市民贊成健康碼設追蹤功能","createTime":"2020-10-28T10:30:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T11:55:33.000Z","uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c2a8ecc9368e833c0b45f636549c3c4b07907c56","tid":2261461,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T10:30:11.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】有調查發現，六成受訪市民贊成恢復通關，當中八成支持推行粵港健康碼互通。<br />\n<br />\n自由黨本月中電話訪問4500名有回鄉卡及智能電話的市民，六成人希望逐步或全面通關，當中分別有八成及七成人支持粵港健康碼互通，及健康碼包含打卡追蹤功能。<br />\n<br />\n自由黨指，調查反映市民不介意加入追蹤功能，有助追蹤病毒來源，並建議數據交予旅發局等第三方獨立管理，而數據必須於香港境內儲存及須遵守私隱條例。<br />\n<br />\n就快可以食探魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=410776\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D410776&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7MIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=3c60240f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D410776&h=5ba5363b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=410776</a>"},{"pid":"44131e50c87ff0f5371818d8cef9d1d430e2d1ae","tid":2261461,"uid":52942,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T10:33:19.000Z","msg":"咁揸回鄉卡個d做囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"010029d86677bc571246cecc3633b9fe4db60b5e","tid":2261461,"uid":331739,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T10:34:13.000Z","msg":"無健康碼 手機裝過支那Apps+返大陸 本來就已經可以由羅湖Track到你去東莞叫雞<br />\n而家只係光明正大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12421a5e6ac4d9cf9ac210d5e24d13797aaebf29","tid":2261461,"uid":214502,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T10:39:00.000Z","msg":"電話訪問4500名有回鄉卡及智能電